snippet.title: Blue Team Launch Trailer | Halo Infinite
snippet.description:
Join Blue Team in Halo Infinite for Operation: Blue Team! Experience Firefight Classic, Hot Swap, and unlock the free 20-tier Operation Pass. Plus, visit the Shop and Exchange for exclusive gear and rewards.  

This event runs until April 8, so get ready for intense battles, legendary rewards, and more!  

https://aka.ms/BlueTeamLaunch
